{"tid":555832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲失業男　屯門友愛邨燒炭亡　","createTime":"2018-02-10T01:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T17:12:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":41,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"d9dbaf78cb6ba35d52022518970ffafda17c7956","tid":555832,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T01:40:39.000Z","msg":"屯門友愛邨愛明樓一單位，早上6時許，一名25歲青年被母親發現，在房間內燒炭自殺，昏迷不醒，連忙報警。救護員到場經檢驗，證實事主已經死亡。據稱，死者從事運輸工作，惟近1個月失業。警方現場撿獲遺書，調查事件沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"aadb42e4e0a33e875150c4b6b0b9927ea1411b85","tid":555832,"uid":169579,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T01:41:36.000Z","msg":"在房間內燒炭自殺聞唔到味？"},{"pid":"ef5c231c57d2971b988bcb853560667935738eb3","tid":555832,"uid":33359,"like":138,"dislike":6,"score":132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T01:42:02.000Z","msg":"一個月姐,一定係個老母日日比說話佢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114bc11b0909d19d15781c608bd902bdfb2f5e68","tid":555832,"uid":10692,"like":76,"dislike":12,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfa944d9b2df8c309c148bca84ee219970609140","tid":555832,"uid":170157,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T01:43:53.000Z","msg":"細個唔讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15dbc4abc446d0692190a7b8ab0e20ae5b054ed","tid":555832,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T01:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e124d02f130c0f302861b45e85ce1c0ec55a0da1","tid":555832,"uid":51701,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cfa944d9b2df8c309c148bca84ee219970609140","tid":555832,"uid":170157,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"